{"tid":684532,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"點解d人可以生勾勾劏野?","createTime":"2018-05-30T15:20:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-31T06:53:11.000Z","uid":173617,"like":4,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"b1150b88476254e1c218bdb452dd0b32261e3477","tid":684532,"uid":173617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T15:20:11.000Z","msg":"諗落都好顛,生勾勾,有眼耳口鼻有反應,識叫識走,一刀放血再肢解,再煮黎食。<br />\n之前日本有片要d學生咁做,有無巴絲試過劏過野?"},{"pid":"1876b0156b1991468d921b5e681a0c5f720f6cf3","tid":684532,"uid":102096,"like":2,"dislike":19,"score":-17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T15:22:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cf65e32700110f572f8f3178598d56aef49a0f98","tid":684532,"uid":10307,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T15:23:11.000Z","msg":"魚類會拍頭先"},{"pid":"6e3f8bedfb494393eeff5c936202b96b87be0280","tid":684532,"uid":173617,"like":28,"dislike":6,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T15:26:08.000Z","msg":"打邊爐生勾勾放隻蝦入爐都唔想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecb1bed4386b9f670580c453b5c7b49218bba969","tid":684532,"uid":53306,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T18:19:43.000Z","msg":"皰丁解牛"},{"pid":"3f502121f6815bc065e0de35faefd9595a9928a6","tid":684532,"uid":172172,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T18:57:42.000Z","msg":"有無巴絲試過劏雀仔?"},{"pid":"65174cbd4e7ee8b91f8aa39ffff96c83c3eb9e5a","tid":684532,"uid":144466,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T19:05:33.000Z","msg":"一次生兩次熟，人都係咁劏啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b107cbf2b4c14ef91c7e07ced16f435b73c1508d","tid":684532,"uid":145208,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T19:08:02.000Z","msg":"認真，無論劏雞定魚，我覺得好殘忍"},{"pid":"84f3344ccac7caa5acc0e2dd78c147779963f33c","tid":684532,"uid":116131,"like":24,"dislike":6,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"6e3f8bedfb494393eeff5c936202b96b87be0280","tid":684532,"uid":173617,"like":28,"dislike":6,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T15:26:08.000Z","msg":"打邊爐生勾勾放隻蝦入爐都唔想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T19:25:16.000Z","msg":"係 所以無食生蝦好耐<br />\n生勾勾比枝竹籤由尾吉入頭仲要未死<br />\n然後再比人用滾水碌死<br />\n<br />\n但唔會阻止朋友食，<br />\n如果朋友有叫既我會快手碌死哂啲蝦<br />\n盡量縮短佢地痛苦既時間<br />\n如果有朋友玩食物一定屌撚佢地幼稚<br />\n例如啲碌一下又拎一下上嚟一定會阻止<br />\n食就食啦玩乜春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7998901feaf1f9356cded457a368333d332ce3c6","tid":684532,"uid":70429,"like":29,"dislike":7,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T19:45:08.000Z","msg":"以前未禁止供應活雞之前我阿媽喺我面前劏過幾次雞...<br />\n<br />\n割頸倒轉放血落洗手盤..<br />\n<br />\n望住佢前幾個鐘仲喺度咯咯咯咁叫,<br />\n<br />\n夜晚食果陣零舍食得唔安樂...<br />\n<br />\n自此之後其實知道我地冇得改變殺生依樣野,<br />\n<br />\n唯有珍惜食物,珍惜佢既犧牲去食佢d肉.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對於廚藝差浪費食物既廚師我會覺得應該捉去打靶."},{"pid":"b177dd688e79efe6feff4b2ca06c30efb895023a","tid":684532,"uid":150421,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T19:57:11.000Z","msg":"所以我唔去街市"},{"pid":"6e170e6e8fdf63eade32ce36ea8a3d4db47e80b9","tid":684532,"uid":98624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T19:57:21.000Z","msg":"聽過水吧佬講話細個個時係層房做啲水吧學徒仔<br />\n啲刀手全裸園裙，成身血咁四圍走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68500c450bb6a7003145c022eb808d01318641ec","tid":684532,"uid":180745,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"84f3344ccac7caa5acc0e2dd78c147779963f33c","tid":684532,"uid":116131,"like":24,"dislike":6,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"6e3f8bedfb494393eeff5c936202b96b87be0280","tid":684532,"uid":173617,"like":28,"dislike":6,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T15:26:08.000Z","msg":"打邊爐生勾勾放隻蝦入爐都唔想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"20